DESCRIPTION:This is an all-levels yoga flow for beginners to experts that w
	ill help you build strength and mobility. The vinyasa flow is set to the b
	eat of the latest top 40 and throwback favorites. The last portion of clas
	s will be all about opening the body and increasing mobility.  Each class 
	will end with a sound bath Shavasana.\n\nhttps://www.levyparkhouston.org/e
	vents/slow-flow-with-stephanie-mccarrey-3-2/2026-06-24/\n\nFrom Levy Park 
	Houston
